fields.subject: AI MODULE FOR RAW MATRIALS INVENTORY MANAGMENT_WEEKLY PROGRESS REPORT_2022.11.01
fields.content:
The manufacturing Execution System (MES) aims to improve the industrial production process

Hence, the goal of this project is to develop an AI-based platform to apply service to the manufacturing process at a minimal cost while improving the productivity of the process.

This project is in 3 phases:

Phase 1: AI Module for raw materials inventory management (2022.07~2022.12)

Phase 2: AI Module for process routing optimization (2023.01~2023.06)

Phase 3: AI Module for anomaly detection in the production process (2023.07~2023.12)
